---
title: Loaded Mexican Beef, Bean & Veggie Bowl with Corn Chips, Cucumber & Sour Cream
description: All the burrito goodness — no wrap required! This burrito bowl is loaded with vibrant flavours: Hearty beans, beef, zesty salsa, crunchy cucumber and a dollop of sour cream. Scoop it up with crunchy corn chips for the ultimate bite!
